psr-4 Composer Autoloading

for a complete information: http://www.php-fig.org/psr/psr-4/

create a json file called "composer.json"

- check if composer is already installed. Composer must be installed globally.
- Choose with Finder "New terminal at folder" to have access within directory to composer.
- Create a directory "Vendor" with Terminal. Write "mkdir Vendor" in Terminal.
- Create a index.php in main directory with the rest directories and files.
- In Terminal write "composer install" to install dependencies.

- After any update in your code use "composer dump-autoload -o" in Terminal.
- Also you can use "composer update"